[TITLE]
PDA demand model + emitter + FAVAD leakage interaction

A single reservoir feeding one junction. The junction has an emitter and
pressure-dependent demand (PDA), while the connecting pipe has FAVAD leakage.
This exercises all three nodal outflow mechanisms concurrently.

[JUNCTIONS]
;ID      Elev   Demand
J1       50     100

[RESERVOIRS]
;ID      Head
R1       200

[PIPES]
;ID  Node1  Node2  Length  Diam  Roughness  MinorLoss  Status
P1   R1     J1     1000    12    100        0          Open

[EMITTERS]
;Junction  Coeff
J1         1.0

[LEAKAGE]
;Pipe  Coeff1  Coeff2
P1     50      0.1

[OPTIONS]
Units                GPM
Headloss             H-W
Demand Model         PDA
Minimum Pressure     0
Required Pressure    30
Pressure Exponent    0.5

[END]
